      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Builder Pattern",
      "fontSize": 72.21492346938761,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Builder Pattern",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-wwyVMHeIJh2WJb7vWmcF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 212.5562307749832,
      "y": 2408.0251665169217,
      "width": 1268.0592041015625,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1971278355,
      "version": 556,
      "versionNonce": 1330973053,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781419221306,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The problem here is that if any Class Constructors have so many parameters: some Required and others Optional, \nthen it gets really difficult to manage and problem of Constructor Overloading occurs.\n\nLike in HTTP Request, we have URL & Method as Required-params and Header, Query-params, Body, Timeout as Optional-params.\nWe want to have all the params in HTTPRequest class and a function called execute() to actually send a request with set config",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The problem here is that if any Class Constructors have so many parameters: some Required and others Optional, \nthen it gets really difficult to manage and problem of Constructor Overloading occurs.\n\nLike in HTTP Request, we have URL & Method as Required-params and Header, Query-params, Body, Timeout as Optional-params.\nWe want to have all the params in HTTPRequest class and a function called execute() to actually send a request with set config",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0ghsUukyBx4R6QN8AIJnK",
