    {
      "id": "ERTo8gf1gpvcvv7jySlcD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 288.5222860351155,
      "y": 2557.2743221650967,
      "width": 457.599365234375,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1132759827,
      "version": 306,
      "versionNonce": 520699571,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781422497768,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "class HTTPRequest {\nprivate:\n    string url;\n    string method;\n    map<string, string> headers;\n    map<string, string> queryParams;\n    ...\n\npublic:\n    HTTPRequest(url, method, headers, ...) {\n        this->url = url;\n        this->method = method;\n        this->headers = headers;\n        ...\n    }\n\n    void execute() {\n        // executes HTTP Request with the set config\n    }\n}",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "class HTTPRequest {\nprivate:\n    string url;\n    string method;\n    map<string, string> headers;\n    map<string, string> queryParams;\n    ...\n\npublic:\n    HTTPRequest(url, method, headers, ...) {\n        this->url = url;\n        this->method = method;\n        this->headers = headers;\n        ...\n    }\n\n    void execute() {\n        // executes HTTP Request with the set config\n    }\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "THQgQnRi0P5Y5NyDaQxTF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 199.10173145765054,
      "y": 2948.514418996084,
      "width": 1261.779296875,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1614567453,
      "version": 672,
      "versionNonce": 985889299,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781422390574,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "But let's say we want to make HTTPRequest with only URL and Method, but we had only 1 constructor which needed everything\nSo to resolve this, we will create new constructor with only URL & Method as in Constructor Overloading \n\nSimilarly for each possible Subset combination, we will require separate Constructors, like:\n- HttpRequest(url, method, headers)\n- HttpRequest(url, method, body)\n- HttpRequest(url, method, headers, body)\n  ...",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "But let's say we want to make HTTPRequest with only URL and Method, but we had only 1 constructor which needed everything\nSo to resolve this, we will create new constructor with only URL & Method as in Constructor Overloading \n\nSimilarly for each possible Subset combination, we will require separate Constructors, like:\n- HttpRequest(url, method, headers)\n- HttpRequest(url, method, body)\n- HttpRequest(url, method, headers, body)\n  ...",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3rHfKXIwfAWxsDIOJnzxu",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 201.75479367285334,
      "y": 3216.668497418827,
      "width": 728.4194946289062,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1940412563,
      "version": 265,
      "versionNonce": 2023110301,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781434291103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Constructor-Overloading/Telescoping is total mess.\n2. We want Class Attributes to be Immutable, though this can be resolved\n    by removing Setters for private fields\n3. Inconsistent State problem (explained below)\n4. Scattered State validation\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Constructor-Overloading/Telescoping is total mess.\n2. We want Class Attributes to be Immutable, though this can be resolved\n    by removing Setters for private fields\n3. Inconsistent State problem (explained below)\n4. Scattered State validation\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Fpat1CE6dKw5Ua-UavVqj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 207.22233004919968,
      "y": 3186.4270510383376,
      "width": 89.93994140625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aB",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1090766845,
      "version": 18,
      "versionNonce": 1057094739,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781422430636,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Problems:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Problems:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PxVtGACT1eRrUg6jZ1gb6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 208.0145835703264,
      "y": 3368.375774629887,
      "width": 761.199462890625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 676508061,
      "version": 201,
      "versionNonce": 995491677,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781431177532,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We can make URL, Method & Headers as required by Constructor \nand set remaining Attributes through Setters befor calling execute() function",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We can make URL, Method & Headers as required by Constructor \nand set remaining Attributes through Setters befor calling execute() function",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Xgi-G3azGN7n_BudHnn10",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 262.75332043487305,
      "y": 3425.6656073763643,
      "width": 492.79931640625,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2006316531,
      "version": 523,
      "versionNonce": 1920469949,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781431177532,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HttpRequest req = new HttpRequest(url, method, headers);\nreq.setQueryParams(queryParams);\nreq.setBody(bodyParams);\n\nreq.execute();",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HttpRequest req = new HttpRequest(url, method, headers);\nreq.setQueryParams(queryParams);\nreq.setBody(bodyParams);\n\nreq.execute();",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7DTmVNBtD-dCnqQrOuqfK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 203.62417864074894,
      "y": 3546.9739260383367,
      "width": 1472.1590576171875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aE",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2049702003,
      "version": 622,
      "versionNonce": 1825154845,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781431498776,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Problem with this approach is that since Setters are optional, so endpoints which required some attribute but didn't received via Setter will blow-up.\nSince we don't have direct means to check and will get RunTime errrors which are avoided as it causes Unexpected behaviour \nwhereas CompileTime errors helps to catch bugs in advance before reaching to public.\n\nTo avoid this issue, we will need to validate for whether the config is valid or not before execute, which will cause Scattered State validation problem",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Problem with this approach is that since Setters are optional, so endpoints which required some attribute but didn't received via Setter will blow-up.\nSince we don't have direct means to check and will get RunTime errrors which are avoided as it causes Unexpected behaviour \nwhereas CompileTime errors helps to catch bugs in advance before reaching to public.\n\nTo avoid this issue, we will need to validate for whether the config is valid or not before execute, which will cause Scattered State validation problem",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "n1Idlax21eN1fCnr7ukyq",
      "type": "ellipse",
      "x": 189.37818619445585,
      "y": 3803.324215996028,
